    {
      "type": "text", "id": "sensor_list",
      "x": 80, "y": 230, "width": 320, "height": 240,
      "text": "• Supply-air thermistor (A0)\n• Return-air thermistor (A1)\n• Compressor CT → bias → (A2)\n• Filter diff-pressure (I²C)\n\nTargets the 3 canonical\nRTU failure modes:\n  – refrigerant loss\n  – short-cycling\n  – clogged filter",
      "originalText": "• Supply-air thermistor (A0)\n• Return-air thermistor (A1)\n• Compressor CT → bias → (A2)\n• Filter diff-pressure (I²C)\n\nTargets the 3 canonical\nRTU failure modes:\n  – refrigerant loss\n  – short-cycling\n  – clogged filter",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
