    {
      "type": "text", "id": "evidence_note",
      "x": 790, "y": 580, "width": 630, "height": 180,
      "text": "Alerts fire on threshold trips:\n  • delta_t_low         (refrigerant loss)\n  • short_cycling       (compressor starts/hr)\n  • filter_dp_high      (clogged filter)\n\nEach alert bypasses the hourly outbound\ntimer via sync:true so the service tech is\npaged in seconds, not at the next window.",
      "originalText": "Alerts fire on threshold trips:\n  • delta_t_low         (refrigerant loss)\n  • short_cycling       (compressor starts/hr)\n  • filter_dp_high      (clogged filter)\n\nEach alert bypasses the hourly outbound\ntimer via sync:true so the service tech is\npaged in seconds, not at the next window.",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
